    "1.12.2-1.5.0": "New Features:\n+ Added Persimmon tree as dying oak subspecies\n+ Added Peach tree as a flowering oak subspecies\n+ Added Pear tree as an oak species\n+ Added seeds for Poplar and Dark Poplar species\n+ Added config settings to disable or enable the features above\n+ Populated xeric shrubland and tundra biomes with acacia and maple twiglets\n+ Mega Umbran Conifer is now the mega variant of the Umbran Conifer, making it obtainable through the use of a Potion of Gigas\nEnhancements:\n+ Added version update checker\n+ Updated water roots to use new model\n+ Updated flowering oak to display flowers during felling animation\n+ Renamed OakFloweringVine to OakIvyVines (as flowering vines were removed)\n+ Updated textures slightly, making them more consistent\nBug Fixes:\n+ Fixed jungle twiglets in oasis not having their proper species\n+ Fixed missing translation for certain species",
